{"tid":1741081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[反送中運動] 被屈叫雞後首發聲　Simon Cheng：在中國受酷刑","createTime":"2019-11-20T07:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T10:41:03.000Z","uid":337146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5058fc0aa923943680b5530e26ed8e8c45a52552","tid":1741081,"uid":337146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:37:39.000Z","msg":"被屈叫雞後首發聲　Simon Cheng：在中國受酷刑<br />\n<br />\n大家還記得Simon Cheng（鄭文傑）嗎？那位在英國領事館工作的港人，8月初在深圳搭乘高鐵回港時被消失。近兩周後中共才證實他被行政拘留，罪名是「嫖妓」。被釋放的Simon Cheng，事隔三個月首度發聲，指在中國遭受酷刑對待。<br />\n<br />\n11月20日，Simon在Facebook發聲明，否認中共以非法程序對他提出的任何罪名，並指控中國當局對他使用酷刑、威脅及脅迫。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，自己在私支持香港的反送中運動，曾協助佐敦的連儂牆，期間並無作出任何非法行為；在公，他協助英國駐香港總領事館收集示威信息，以便評估旅行警報，及是否涉及英國公民。他因此加入telegram及監視新聞與連登，並與示威者接觸。他更認識一些在港參與示威的中國人，當中一些人被香港警察逮捕，隨後保釋。<br />\n<br />\nSimon指出，自己未從創傷中恢復，並恐怕會面臨更大報復，所以不對此案作進一步評論。他又強調，對中國的司法系統無信心，在經歷過如斯可怕經歷後，不會尋求司法協助。<br />\n<br />\n被捕過程：<br />\n<br />\n2019年8月8日，Simon在深圳出差後去按摩放鬆，及後與一位內地示威者的父母見面，助這名示威者取得生活費，應付香港的司法程序。他期間有向女友報告行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n他在深圳福田乘坐高鐵回港，在西九高鐵站的中國關口過境時被攔住，有身穿制服的公安稱上頭命令阻止他出境。<br />\n<br />\nSimon拒絕提供iPhone密碼的要求（電話包含敏感的工作信息及私人對話）。他及後被押上高鐵送回深圳，並福田派出所遭粗暴的便衣警察審問。<br />\n<br />\n聲明連結：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/notes/cheng-man-kit/for-the-record-an-enemy-of-the-state/2490959950941845/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnotes%2Fcheng-man-kit%2Ffor-the-record-an-enemy-of-the-state%2F2490959950941845%2F&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=148dca2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/notes/cheng-man-kit/for-the-record-an-enemy-of-the-state/2490959950941845/</a><br />\n<br />\n《BBC》報道：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-50457262\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-50457262&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=213d8e98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-50457262&h=782ac17c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-50457262</a><br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.wsj.com/articles/former-u-k-consulate-employee-says-chinese-secret-police-tortured-him-11574229602\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2Fformer-u-k-consulate-employee-says-chinese-secret-police-tortured-him-11574229602&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLA8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=1fb7332c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.wsj.com/articles/former-u-k-consulate-employee-says-chinese-secret-police-tortured-him-11574229602</a><br />\n<br />\nVia WhatsApp; 休班記者"},{"pid":"b91d622cf2403c206b32bd6496969ffaa35357ac","tid":1741081,"uid":55583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T07:51:19.000Z","msg":"屈叫雞擺明就係人格謀殺想冇人再信佢講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0b862e1fc3337d401d67ca85ac2d7c134084693","tid":1741081,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:16:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7c4631e3d49ed96354a8d8a0c49350a5e9cf80d","tid":1741081,"uid":242998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"出差後按摩？按摩定出火？三個月後先講，你day 1返香港爆大鑊就有人信。"},{"pid":"a070a84de4eb6f2ce74251bb86d627632c5b2ead","tid":1741081,"uid":337146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a7c4631e3d49ed96354a8d8a0c49350a5e9cf80d","tid":1741081,"uid":242998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T10:44:57.000Z","msg":"出差後按摩？按摩定出火？三個月後先講，你day 1返香港爆大鑊就有人信。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T02:33:29.000Z","msg":"又一五毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7c622c16afa5b990cc03b01cb225eb0310789f","tid":1741081,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T06:16:51.000Z","msg":"<span st